  <brief_title>Study Evaluating &quot;Real World&quot; Treatment Pattern in Previously Treated Hemophilia A Patients Receiving KOVALTRY (Octocog Alfa) for Routine Prophylaxis</brief_title>
  <acronym>TAURUS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multinational Phase IV Study Evaluating &quot;Real World&quot; Treatment Pattern in Previously Treated Hemophilia A Patients Receiving KOVALTRY (Octocog Alfa) for Routine Prophylaxis</official_title>
